    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total dream! It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s been kept perfectly tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Can't wait for it to go to a great new home!",
