    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically superlative: the VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential and suspension bushings remain in factory-fresh condition, providing the tactile feedback and telepathic turn-in these chassis are renowned for. Finished in impeccable paint with an unblemished interior, this is a turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless paint. Interior like new. Low mileage. Full service records included. No accidents.",
      "price": 43500.0,
