    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that stands in impeccable, showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since its initial purchase, preserving its original integrity. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin feels like a time capsule; the premium upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, the dashboard is pristine, and every electronic feature operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented in a comprehensive service history folder. With an undercarriage as clean as the bodywork and a smooth, silent ride that mirrors its first day on the road, this is arguably the finest example available for a discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present an automotive specimen of unrivaled preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, having been meticulously maintained to ensure every detail adheres to the highest standards of excellence. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, this motorcar offers an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
