    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of this car, and it\u2019s honestly in flawless shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day I drove it off the lot. Not a single blemish to be found, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, but it's time for a new home. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
