    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1993 Mazda RX-7 (FD), a masterclass in front-midship balance and rotary precision. This example features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine, delivering linear power delivery across the rev range with zero boost leaks. Chassis rigidity remains factory-spec, complemented by a four-wheel double-wishbone suspension that minimizes unsprung mass for exceptional lateral transients. The Torsen limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque vectoring under load. Recent compression testing shows uniform high-PSI results across all rotor faces, confirming the integrity of the apex seals. With a factory-original interior and a flawlessly preserved undercarriage, this FD represents a rare convergence of mechanical excellence and aesthetic purity.",
